This project is based on guidance published by the G7 Cybersecurity Working
Group ("Software Bill of Materials for AI — Minimum Elements", February 2026).
The G7 document itself is the work of public authorities and is referenced for
its content. Field descriptions in this tool are condensed paraphrases of the
G7 source for inline display; users should consult the original document for
